The '''C-2 [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]]''' was a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] manufactured on the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Telti/Legends|Telti]] by [[Cybot Galactica/Legends|Cybot Galactica]]. It was programmed with many functions and forms of communication. It was the successor of the [[C-1 protocol droid]] and the predecessor of the [[C-3 protocol droid]].

